: # Delta Spec: AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架\\n2: \\n3: ## Overview\\n4: \\n5: This delta-spec defines acceptance scenarios for implementing the WorkloadManager HTTP service framework in `pkg/workloadmanager`.\\n6: \\n7: ## Base Specifications\\n8: \\n9: - **AR**: AR-004\\n10: - **Module**: `pkg/workloadmanager`\\n11: - **Language**: Go\\n12: - **Size**: M\\n13: \\n14: ---\\n15: \\n16: ## Scenario: HTTP Server Foundation\\n17: \\n18: ### AR-004-001: Server initialization\\n19: \\n20: - **GIVEN** a Go package at `pkg/workloadmanager`\\n21: - **WHEN** creating HTTP server initialization\\n22: - **THEN** the server SHALL embed necessary HTTP handlers\\n23: - **AND** SHALL expose configurable listen address\\n24: \\n25: ### AR-004-002: Health check endpoint\\n26: \\n27: - **GIVEN** HTTP server running\\n28: - **WHEN** health check endpoint is accessed\\n29: - **THEN** it SHALL return appropriate health status\\n30: \\n31: ---\\n32: \\n33: ## Scenario: Workload Management API\\n34: \\n35: ### AR-004-003: Create workload endpoint\\n36: \\n37: - **GIVEN** HTTP server with workload management\\n38: - **WHEN** POST request to create workload\\n39: - **THEN** the workload SHALL be created successfully\\n40: \\n41: ### AR-004-004: Get workload endpoint\\n42: \\n43: - **GIVEN** existing workloads\\n44: - **WHEN** GET request for specific workload\\n45: - **THEN** it S...\n  Line 26: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775841425162,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2879ab85effeNL1ZUUbsvQv248\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7865b3160015fra6BDTx1JKJC\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7865a7cd001sgh1RNNgYOOGBO\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2879ab85effeNL1ZUUbsvQv248\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_bad97d4dfe61467680d6d759\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/proposal.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/proposal.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # Proposal: AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP Service Framework\\n2: \\n3: ## Summary\\n4: \\n5: Implement an HTTP service framework in `pkg/workloadmanager` that exposes RESTful APIs for managing AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter Kubernetes resources. The service integrates with the `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go` library to provide CRUD operations and watch functionality.\\n6: \\n7: ## Purpose\\n8: \\n9: ### Background\\n10: The WorkloadManager module needs to expose its functionality via HTTP APIs for external clients and internal services to interact with AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter resources in the Kubernetes cluster.\\n11: \\n12: ### Goal\\n13: Provide a production-ready HTTP service framework that:\\n14: - Serves RESTful APIs for AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter CRUD operations\\n15: - Integrates with the `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go` library for Kubernetes API access\\n16: - Follows Kubernetes controller patterns and best practices\\n17: \\n18: ### Value\\n19: - Enables external systems to manage AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter resources programmatically\\n20: - Provides a standardized HTTP interface layer on top of the Kubernetes client\\n21: - Supports observability, middleware extensibility, and graceful shutdown\\n22: \\n23: ---\\n24: \\n25: ## Scope\\n26: \\n27: ### In-Scope\\n28: \\n29: | Deliverable | Description |\\n30: |-------------|-...\n  Line 30: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775841496658,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2879ab85effeNL1ZUUbsvQv248\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7865d02f001MoFRzFPVUUtFOk\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7865b73d001AlF0O3SvewIpNQ\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2879ab85effeNL1ZUUbsvQv248\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"edit\",\"callID\":\"toolu_dd2cb63150cd487aa2137829\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-004/delta-spec.md\",\"newString\":\"# Delta Spec: AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架\\n\\n## Overview\\n\\nThis delta-spec defines acceptance scenarios for implementing the WorkloadManager HTTP service framework in `pkg/workloadmanager`.\\n\\n## Base Specifications\\n\\n- **AR**: AR-004\\n- **Module**: `pkg/workloadmanager`\\n- **Language**: Go\\n- **Size**: M\\n- **Depends On**: `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go` (clientset, informers, listers)\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Scenario: HTTP Server Foundation\\n\\n### AR-004-001: Server initialization\\n\\n- **GIVEN** a Go package at `pkg/workloadmanager`\\n- **WHEN** creating HTTP server initialization\\n- **THEN** the server SHALL embed necessary HTTP handlers\\n- **AND** SHALL expose configurable listen address via `--port` flag (default 8080)\\n- **AND** SHALL support graceful shutdown within 30 seconds\\n\\n### AR-004-002: Health check endpoints\\n\\n- **GIVEN** HTTP server running on configured port\\n- **WHEN** client sends GET request to `/healthz`\\n- **THEN** it SHALL return HTTP 200 OK with status \\\"ok\\\"\\n- **AND** SHALL return Content-Type `text/plain`\\n\\n- **GIVEN** HTTP server running on configured port\\n- **WHEN** client sends GET request to `/readyz`\\n- - **THEN** it SHALL return HTTP 200 OK when server is ready to serve traffic\\n- **AND** it SHALL return HTTP 503 Service Unavailable when not ready\\n\\n### AR-004-003: Server configuration via flags\\n\\n- **GIVEN** workloadmanager binary with flag parsing\\n- **WHEN** started with `--port=9090`\\n- **THEN** the HTTP server SHALL listen on port 90...\n  Line 33: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775841507989,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2879ab85effeNL1ZUUbsvQv248\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7866eb3d001GaP5qgqvMTqifO\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7866ce9b001ioCGRrFzQZasdp\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2879ab85effeNL1ZUUbsvQv248\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The delta-spec.md has been expanded with comprehensive GIVEN/WHEN/THEN scenarios covering:\\n\\n- **HTTP Server Foundation** (AR-004-001 to 003): Server initialization, health endpoints, flag configuration\\n- **Kubernetes Client Integration** (AR-004-010 to 012): kubeconfig, in-cluster, resource cleanup\\n- **AgentRuntime CRUD API** (AR-004-020 to 027): Create, Get, List, Update, Delete, Status, Patch, Watch\\n- **CodeInterpreter CRUD API** (AR-004-030 to 037): Same operations as AgentRuntime\\n- **Middleware & Observability** (AR-004-040 to 042): Logging, metrics, error handling\\n- **API Format & Compatibility** (AR-004-050 to 051): JSON content type, Kubernetes error format\\n- **Integration with client-go** (AR-004-060 to 062): Clientset, Informers, Listers usage\\n- **ClusterRole & RBAC** (AR-004-070): Required permissions\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775841507988,\"end\":1775841507988}}}\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z_logs/AR-004_ST-4.log:\n  Line 4: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775841317294,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2879c023bffeQf7J1q9dvjfwyr\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d786409a30014lO75g0o3i7lLK\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7863feb0001q3g1lxFLkqwQ9k\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2879c023bffeQf7J1q9dvjfwyr\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"glob\",\"callID\":\"toolu_6affdc8bdb7b449f930e8ad6\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"pattern\":\"**/AR-004*.md\"},\"output\":\"No files found\",\"metadata\":{\"count\":0,\"truncated\":false},\"title\":\"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775841317268,\"end\":1775841317292}}}}\n  Line 7: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775841317303,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2879c023bffeQf7J1q9dvjfwyr\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d78641045001RkfP03jgsQq7aT\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7863feb0001q3g1lxFLkqwQ9k\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2879c023bffeQf7J1q9dvjfwyr\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"glob\",\"callID\":\"toolu_8d381bd2b5744999ae1f9f39\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"pattern\":\"**/*.md\"},\"output\":\"/home/