e.volcano.sh` / `v1alpha1`**, module path **`github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go`**. Source reference: `/tmp/agentcube-ref/client-go/`.\\n13: \\n14: ## Clientset\\n15: \\n16: ### `Interface` (`clientset/versioned/clientset.go`)\\n17: \\n18: ```go\\n19: type Interface interface {\\n20: \\tDiscovery() discovery.DiscoveryInterface\\n21: \\tRuntimeV1alpha1() runtimev1alpha1.RuntimeV1alpha1Interface\\n22: }\\n23: ```\\n24: \\n25: ### `Clientset` struct\\n26: \\n27: Embeds `*discovery.DiscoveryClient` and holds `runtimeV1alpha1 *runtimev1alpha1.RuntimeV1alpha1Client`.\\n28: \\n29: **Constructors**\\n30: \\n31: - `NewForConfig(c *rest.Config) (*Clientset, error)`\\n32: - `NewForConfigAndClient(c *rest.Config, httpClient *http.Client) (*Clientset, error)`\\n33: - `NewForConfigOrDie(c *rest.Config) *Clientset`\\n34: - `New(c rest.Interface) *Clientset`\\n35: \\n36: **Group accessor:** `RuntimeV1alpha1() runtimev1alpha1.RuntimeV1alpha1Interface`\\n37: \\n38: ---\\n39: \\n40: ## Typed client — `runtime/v1alpha1`\\n41: \\n42: ### `RuntimeV1alpha1Interface` (`clientset/ve...\n  Line 7: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775841339513,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2879c0ebbffeE6Frd5ny1RkJ5L\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d78641af8001MKmnA6cg5QtYK9\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d786409f2001L82y7nwz76DzIK\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2879c0ebbffeE6Frd5ny1RkJ5L\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"toolu_27089e2343c1450694551689\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"error\",\"input\":{\"content\":\"# Proposal: WorkloadManager HTTP Service Framework\\n\\n## AR Information\\n- **AR ID**: AR-004\\n- **Title**: WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架\\n- **Module**: pkg/workloadmanager\\n- **Language**: Go\\n- **Size**: M\\n\\n## 1. Purpose\\n\\n### Background\\nThe WorkloadManager module needs to expose its functionality via HTTP APIs for external clients and internal services to interact with AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter resources in the Kubernetes cluster.\\n\\n### Goal\\nProvide a production-ready HTTP service framework in `pkg/workloadmanager` that:\\n- Serves RESTful APIs for AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter CRUD operations\\n- Integrates with the `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go` library for Kubernetes API access\\n- Follows Kubernetes controller patterns and best practices\\n\\n### Value\\n- Enables external systems to manage AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter resources programmatically\\n- Provides a standardized HTTP interface layer on top of the Kubernetes client\\n- Supports observability, middleware extensibility, and graceful shutdown\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 2. Scope\\n\\n### In-Scope\\n1. **HTTP Server Implementation**\\n   - HTTP server with configurable host/port\\n   - Graceful shutdown handling\\n   - Health check endpoints (`/healthz`, `/readyz`)\\n\\n2. **REST API Endpoints**\\n   - AgentRuntime CRUD: `GET/POST/PUT/DELETE /api/v1/namespaces/{namespace}/agentruntimes`\\n   - AgentRuntime status: `GET/PATCH /api/v1/namespaces/{namespace}/agentruntimes/{name}/status`\\n   - CodeInterpreter CRUD: `GET/POST/PUT/DELETE /api/v1/namespaces/{namespace}/codeinterpreters`\\n   - CodeInterpreter status: `GET/PATCH /api/v1/namespaces/{namespace}/codeinterpreters/{nam...\n  Line 13: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775841387376,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2879c0ebbffeE6Frd5ny1RkJ5L\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d78648a8c0016SADrSvU8X7jpD\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d78647afe001GC4BREGHt2cjmH\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2879c0ebbffeE6Frd5ny1RkJ5L\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"toolu_d7ff5b1d87084365901f50a4\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"content\":\"# Proposal: AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP Service Framework\\n\\n## Summary\\n\\nImplement an HTTP service framework in `pkg/workloadmanager` that exposes RESTful APIs for managing AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter Kubernetes resources. The service integrates with the `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go` library to provide CRUD operations and watch functionality.\\n\\n## Purpose\\n\\n### Background\\nThe WorkloadManager module needs to expose its functionality via HTTP APIs for external clients and internal services to interact with AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter resources in the Kubernetes cluster.\\n\\n### Goal\\nProvide a production-ready HTTP service framework that:\\n- Serves RESTful APIs for AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter CRUD operations\\n- Integrates with the `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go` library for Kubernetes API access\\n- Follows Kubernetes controller patterns and best practices\\n\\n### Value\\n- Enables external systems to manage AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter resources programmatically\\n- Provides a standardized HTTP interface layer on top of the Kubernetes client\\n- Supports observability, middleware extensibility, and graceful shutdown\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Scope\\n\\n### In-Scope\\n\\n| Deliverable | Description |\\n|-------------|-------------|\\n| HTTP Server | Configurable host/port with graceful shutdown |\\n| Health Endpoints | `/healthz`, `/readyz` for liveness/readiness probes |\\n| REST API Endpoints | CRUD operations for AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter |\\n| Client Integration | Integration with client-go Clientset |\\n| Middleware | Request logging, metrics, error handling |\\n\\n### API Endpoints\\n\\n#### Agen...\n  Line 16: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775841394479,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2879c0ebbffeE6Frd5ny1RkJ5L\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d78653b85001cUqv6IGsFmGdTB\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d78652397001Jw5paRuJlo1LZa\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2879c0ebbffeE6Frd5ny1RkJ5L\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Done. Created `proposal.md` for AR-004 (WorkloadManager HTTP Service Framework) with:\\n\\n- **Purpose**: HTTP service to expose AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter CRUD APIs\\n- **Scope**: HTTP server, REST endpoints, client-go integration, middleware\\n- **Impact Analysis**: Dependencies, consumers, risks\\n- **Alternatives Considered**: net/http (selected), Gin/Echo, K8s aggregation, gRPC\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775841394477,\"