\\n42: ---\\n43: \\n44: ## Requirement: AgentRuntime CRUD API\\n45: \\n46: **ID:** REQ-002  \\n47: **Priority:** P0  \\n48: \\n49: 系统 MUST 提供 AgentRuntime 资源的 CRUD HTTP 端点。\\n50: \\n51: ### Scenario: 创建 AgentRuntime\\n52: \\n53: **GIVEN** 有效的 AgentRuntime 创建请求体（JSON）  \\n54: **WHEN** 发送 `POST /api/v1/agentruntimes`  \\n55: **THEN** 返回 201 Created  \\n56: **AND** 响应体包含创建的 AgentRuntime 对...\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z_logs/AR-008_ST-1.log:\n  Line 8: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775823066644,\"sessionID\":\"ses_288b6174dffe0vBM04EEI0J8t9\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d774a02a2001dvaKRSA5tS6RFB\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7749f4940013hMWV3EZsKbroF\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_288b6174dffe0vBM04EEI0J8t9\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"task\",\"callID\":\"call_d5504b5e7a204aabb54f4ce8\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"description\":\"Explore workloadmanager module\",\"prompt\":\"Thoroughly explore the codebase at /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z to understand:\\n\\n1. The structure of pkg/workloadmanager - find all Go files, understand the module's purpose\\n2. Any existing GC (garbage collection) or cleanup mechanisms\\n3. How sandboxes/workloads are created, tracked, and deleted\\n4. Any existing timer-based or cron-based mechanisms\\n5. The AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter CRD types and their lifecycle\\n6. Any existing proposals or design docs in the repo\\n7. The overall project structure\\n\\nReturn:\\n- Full directory listing of pkg/workloadmanager\\n- Key types and interfaces found\\n- Any existing GC/cleanup code\\n- How workloads are currently managed (create/delete lifecycle)\\n- Any relevant configuration or constants\\n- Other proposal.md files as examples of format\",\"subagent_type\":\"explore\"},\"output\":\"task_id: ses_288b5e792ffeV8VKHRp1prb0hf (for resuming to continue this task if needed)\\n\\n<task_result>\\nNow I have a comprehensive understanding of the codebase. Here is my complete analysis:\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Comprehensive Codebase Analysis: AgentCube WorkloadManager\\n\\n### 1. Overall Project Structure\\n\\n```\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/\\n├── changes/                    # Change proposals (AR-001 through AR-008)\\n│   ├── AR-001/                 # CRD AgentRuntime type definition\\n│   ├── AR-002/                 # CRD CodeInterpreter type definition\\n│   ├── AR-003/                 # CRD shared types and constants\\n│   ├── AR-004/                 ...\n  Line 12: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775823073078,\"sessionID\":\"ses_288b6174dffe0vBM04EEI0J8t9\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d774daafc001X8BFHJQdq03f2s\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d774d9662001s90EU1vJ7pJauN\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_288b6174dffe0vBM04EEI0J8t9\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_744718325da94eb99b565307\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-007/proposal.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-007/proposal.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-007: K8s Reconciler 控制器\\n2: \\n3: ## 概述\\n4: \\n5: 为 `pkg/workloadmanager` 模块实现 Kubernetes Reconciler 控制器，基于 client-go 生成的 Informer/Lister/Typed Client 构建 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter CR 的调和循环。本控制器监听 `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1` API 组下的自定义资源变更事件，将 K8s 资源状态与 Store（Redis/Valkey）中的会话状态进行调和，是 AgentCube 控制面的核心驱动引擎。本变更是 AR-005（Sandbox 创建）和 AR-006（Sandbox 删除）的上游基础设施，为 handler 层提供事件驱动的调和能力。\\n6: \\n7: ## 元信息\\n8: \\n9: - **Module**: pkg/workloadmanager\\n10: - **Language**: Go\\n11: - **Size**: L\\n12: \\n13: ## 目的\\n14: \\n15: 当前 WorkloadManager 的 handler 层（SandboxCreateHandler、SandboxDeleteHandler）以 HTTP 请求为驱动执行一次性操作，缺少对 Kubernetes 资源状态变化的持续监听和自动调和能力。Reconciler 控制器填补这一空白，实现以下目标：\\n16: \\n17: 1. 通过 `SharedInformerFactory` 监听 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter CR 的创建、更新、删除事件\\n18: 2. 将 CR 状态变更同步到 Store，保持会话状态与 K8s 资源的一致性\\n19: 3. 处理 Pod 生命周期事件（Pending → Running → Terminated），自动更新 Store 中的 Sandbox 状态\\n20: 4. 实现最终一致性：当 Store 与 K8s 资源状态不一致时，通过调和循环自动修复\\n21: 5. 为 GC 循环提供事件驱动的触发机制（资源删除事件立即触发 Store 清理，而非等待 15s tick）\\n22: 6. 支持优雅启动和关闭：Informer 缓存同步完成后再开始调和，关闭时等待队列中的调和任务完成\\n23: \\n24: ## 范围\\n25: \\n26: ### 包含\\n27: \\n28: 1. **Reconciler 结构体** — `SandboxReconciler` 封装 typed client、informer factory、lister、store、workqueue 等依赖\\n29: 2. **Informer 注册** — 通过 `SharedInformerFactory` 注册 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter 的 informer，设置事件回调（AddFunc、UpdateFunc、DeleteFunc）\\n30: ...\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z_logs/AR-008_ST-0.log:\n  Line 7: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775822789366,\"sessionID\":\"ses_288b6bd65ffe2t3J3JFfYlvNuQ\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d774956b80017UaTKFnpCtkayo\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d774950010010AYU18HNEC5tQq\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_288b6bd65ffe2t3J3JFfYlvNuQ\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_2c9b350815f64f5f9ba4c684\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes</path>\\n<type>directory</type>\\n<entries>\\nAR-001/\\nAR-002/\\nAR-003/\\nAR-004/\\nAR-005/\\nAR-006/\\nAR-007/\\n\\n(7 entries)\\n</entries>\",\"metadata\":{\"preview\":\"AR-001/\\nAR-002/\\nAR-003/\\nAR-004/\\nAR-005/\\nAR-006/\\nAR-007/\",\"truncated\":false,\"loaded\":[]},\"title\":\"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775822789361,\"end\":1775822789364}}}}\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z_logs/AR-007_ST-4.log:\n  Line 5: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775821176827,\"sessionID\":\"ses_288d2588effer1XcyOp729BuBT\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d772db47a0015q6klikYpERGq6\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d772da853001KcAPpX2608FoCb\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_288d2588effer1XcyOp729BuBT\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"task\",\"callID\":\"call_4b691739205c4a18889e5f81\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"description\":\"Explore agentcube project structure\",\"prompt\":\"Explore the agentcube project thoroughly. I need to understand:\\n\\n1. The overall project structure - find the root directory and key folders\\n2. The pkg/workloadmanager module - what files exist there, what's already implemented\\n3. Any existing reconciler patterns or K8s controller code in the project\\n4. Any existing tasks.md files or planning documents that show the format used\\n5. Any ST-3 design documents or specs related to AR-007\\n6. The Go module structure (go.mod, imports, dependencies)\\n7. Any existing K8s types, APIs, or controller-runtime usage\\n8. Test patterns used in the project\\n\\nSearch broadly - check for directories like \\\"agentcube\\\", \\\"pkg/\\\", \\\"docs/\\\", \\\"specs/\\\", \\\"plans/\\\", etc. Look for any files mentioning \\\"reconciler\\\", \\\"workloadmanager\\\", \\\"AR-007\\\", \\\"ST-3\\\", \\\"k8s\\\", \\\"controller\\\".\\n\\nReturn a comprehensive summary of:\\n- Project root path\\n- Full directory tree of pkg/workloadmanager\\n- Any existing reconciler/controller code patterns\\n- Format of any existing tasks.md or planning docs\\n- K8s dependencies and versions used\\n- Test framework and patterns\\n- Any design docs for ST-3 or AR-007\",\"subagent_type\":\"explore\"},\"output\":\"task_id: ses_288d23579ffeCqJKrqCu4YiGK5 (for resuming to continue this task if needed)\\n\\n<task_result>\\nI now have a comprehensive understanding of the project. Here is the full summary:\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Comprehensive Project Exploration Summary\\n\\n### 1. Project Root Path\\n\\n```\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z\\n```\\n\\n**Module:** `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube`...\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z_logs/AR-007_ST-3.log:\n  Line 12: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775820794266,\"sessionID\":\"ses_288d870f2ffezxRdNAdSJ3B4AB\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d772ae4c50015XyqRtE5xyRJfW\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d772ad7f5001ITqvjO9ZirZUln\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_288d870f2ffezxRdNAdSJ3B4AB\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_b6955a58bca7495b808af783\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-007/proposal.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-007/proposal.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-007: K8s Reconciler 控制器\\n2: \\n3: ## 概述\\n4: \\n5: 为 `pkg/workloadmanager` 模块实现 Kubernetes Reconciler 控制器，基于 client-go 生成的 Informer/Lister/Typed Client 构建 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter CR 的调和循环。本控制器监听 `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1` API 组下的自定义资源变更事件，将 K8s 资源状态与 Store（Redis/Valkey）中的会话状态进行调和，是 AgentCube 控制面的核心驱动引擎。本变更是 AR-005（Sandbox 创建）和 AR-006（Sandbox 删除）的上游基础设施，为 handler 层提供事件驱动的调和能力。\\n6: \\n7: ## 元信息\\n8: \\n9: - **Module**: pkg/workloadmanager\\n10: - **Language**: Go\\n11: - **Size**: L\\n12: \\n13: ## 目的\\n14: \\n15: 当前 WorkloadManager 的 handler 层（SandboxCreateHandler、SandboxDeleteHandler）以 HTTP 请求为驱动执行一次性操作，缺少对 Kubernetes 资源状态变化的持续监听和自动调和能力。Reconciler 控制器填补这一空白，实现以下目标：\\n16: \\n17: 1. 通过 `SharedInformerFactory` 监听 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter CR 的创建、更新、删除事件\\n18: 2. 将 CR 状态变更同步到 Store，保持会话状态与 K8s 资源的一致性\\n19: 3. 处理 Pod 生命周期事件（Pending → Running → Terminated），自动更新 Store 中的 Sandbox 状态\\n20: 4. 实现最终一致性：当 Store 与 K8s 资源状态不一致时，通过调和循环自动修复\\n21: 5. 为 GC 循环提供事件驱动的触发机制（资源删除事件立即触发 Store 清理，而非等待 15s tick）\\n22: 6. 支持优雅启动和关闭：Informer 缓存同步完成后再开始调和，关闭时等待队列中的调和任务完成\\n23: \\n24: ## 范围\\n25: \\n26: ### 包含\\n27: \\n28: 1. **Reconciler 结构体** — `SandboxReconciler` 封装 typed client、informer factory、lister、store、workqueue 等依赖\\n29: 2. **Informer 注册** — 通过 `SharedInformerFactory` 注册 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter 的 informer，设置事件回调（AddFunc、UpdateFunc、DeleteFunc）\\n30: ...\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z_logs/AR-007_ST-2.log:\n  Line 7: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775820384057,\"sessionID\":\"ses_288db7c39ffeZ1l0ExGm1Z4v9I\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7724a2cb0019QqH7jUYitgYjJ\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d77248faf001S1H2IOsB3OpeG8\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_288db7c39ffeZ1l0ExGm1Z4v9I\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"glob\",\"callID\":\"call_7319f9b90ee846499c4eeed4\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"path\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z\",\"pattern\":\"**/*\"},\"output\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/.sdd_prompt.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-007/proposal.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-007/tasks.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-007/delta-spec.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-007/design.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/workloadmanager/response/response_test.go\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/workloadmanager/handler/sandbox_lifecycle.go\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/workloadmanager/handler/sandbox_lifecycle_test.go\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/workloadmanager/handler/sandbox_create.go\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/client-go/informers/externalversions/factory.go\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/workloadmanager/handler/sandbox_delete_test.go\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/workloadmanager/handler/sandbo...\n  Line 11: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775820390983,\"sessionID\":\"ses_288db7c39ffeZ1l0ExGm1Z4v9I\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7724bddd001gfPRY6LkFBYIkO\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7724a795001SG2qYLYCHGUXto\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_288db7c39ffeZ1l0ExGm1Z4v9I\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_8b6a1dad83434e9193a07d3a\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-007/proposal.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-007/proposal.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-007: K8s Reconciler 控制器\\n2: \\n3: ## 概述\\n4: \\n5: 为 `pkg/workloadmanager` 模块实现 Kubernetes Reconciler 控制器，基于 client-go 生成的 Informer/Lister/Typed Client 构建 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter CR 的调和循环。本控制器监听 `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1` API 组下的自定义资源变更事件，将 K8s 资源状态与 Store（Redis/Valkey）中的会话状态进行调和，是 AgentCube 控制面的核心驱动引擎。本变更是 AR-005（Sandbox 创建）和 AR-006（Sandbox 删除）的上游基础设施，为 handler 层提供事件驱动的调和能力。\\n6: \\n7: ## 元信息\\n8: \\n9: - **Module**: pkg/workloadmanager\\n10: - **Language**: Go\\n11: - **Size**: L\\n12: \\n13: ## 目的\\n14: \\n15: 当前 WorkloadManager 的 handler 层（SandboxCreateHandler、SandboxDeleteHandler）以 HTTP 请求为驱动执行一次性操作，缺少对 Kubernetes 资源状态变化的持续监听和自动调和能力。Reconciler 控制器填补这一空白，实现以下目标：\\n16: \\n17: 1. 通过 `SharedInformerFactory` 监听 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter CR 的创建、更新、删除事件\\n18: 2. 将 CR 状态变更同步到 Store，保持会话状态与 K8s 资源的一致性\\n19: 3. 处理 Pod 生命周期事件（Pending → Running → Terminated），自动更新 Store 中的 Sandbox 状态\\n20: 4. 实现最终一致性：当 Store 与 K8s 资源状态不一致时，通过调和循环自动修复\\n21: 5. 为 GC 循环提供事件驱动的触发机制（资源删除事件立即触发 Store 清理，而非等待 15s tick）\\n22: 6. 支持优雅启动和关闭：Informer 缓存同步完成后再开始调和，关闭时等待队列中的调和任务完成\\n23: \\n24: ## 范围\\n25: \\n26: ### 包含\\n27: \\n28: 1. **Reconciler 结构体** — `SandboxReconciler` 封装 typed client、informer factory、lister、store、workqueue 等依赖\\n29: 2. **Informer 注册** — 通过 `SharedInformerFactory` 注册 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter 的 informer，设置事件回调（AddFunc、UpdateFunc、DeleteFunc）\\n30: ...\n  Line 17: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775820398135,\"sessionID\":\"ses_288db7c39ffeZ1l0ExGm1Z4v9I\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7724d9f8001G9Fh0nQHKFlqNM\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7724cd31001v4mPc43DmfDCeY\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_288db7c39ffeZ1l0ExGm1Z4v9I\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_3713c08030754b5b88ee9441\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-005/delta-spec.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-005/delta-spec.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-005: Sandbox 创建处理器 — Delta Spec\\n2: \\n3: ## Purpose\\n4: \\n5: 为 `pkg/workloadmanager` 模块实现 Sandbox 创建处理器，将 `POST /v1/agent-runtime` 和 `POST /v1/code-interpreter` 的 HTTP 请求转化为 Kubernetes Sandbox/SandboxClaim CR 资源的创建操作。本变更是 AR-004（HTTP 服务框架）的下游实现，覆盖请求验证、CR 构建、dynamic client 创建、状态等待（watcher 机制）、Pod IP 解析、Store 状态同步、失败回滚、CodeInterpreter Warm Pool 及 Auth 模式处理。\\n6: \\n7: ## Requirements\\n8: \\n9: ### Requirement: SandboxCreateHandler 结构体与依赖注入\\n10: \\n11: The system SHALL define `SandboxCreateHandler` 结构体，封装以下依赖：dynamic client（用于创建 Sandbox/SandboxClaim CR）、typed clientset（用于读取 AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter 模板）、informer factory（用于 informer cache 读取）、Store 接口（用于会话状态持久化）、SandboxReconciler watcher 接口（用于一次性状态等待）、token cache（用于认证场景下的用户 client 缓存）、以及可选的 user client 工厂（EnableAuth 时使用）。\\n12: \\n13: #### Scenario: Handler 构造\\n14: - **GIVEN** 所有必需依赖（dynamic client、typed clientset、informer factory、Store、watcher 接口）均已初始化\\n15: - **WHEN** `NewSandboxCreateHandler(deps)` 被调用\\n16: - **THEN** 返回非空的 `*SandboxCreateHandler` 且所有依赖字段已正确赋值\\n17: \\n18: #### Scenario: 可选依赖为 nil 时不 panic\\n19: - **GIVEN** token cache 或 user client 工厂为 nil（EnableAuth=false 场景）\\n20: - **WHEN** Handler 构造完成\\n21: - **THEN** 不 panic，相关字段为 nil，后续代码路径在 EnableAuth=false 时不访问这些字段\\n22: \\n23: ---\\n24: \\n25: ### Requirement: GVR 常量定义\\n26: \\n27: The system SHALL 定义以下 `schema.GroupVersionResource` 常量...\n  Line 18: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775820399491,\"sessionID\":\"ses_288db7c39ffeZ1l0ExGm1Z4v9I\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7724defa00108938xjlBs63Tl\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7724cd31001v4mPc43DmfDCeY\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_288db7c39ffeZ1l0ExGm1Z4v9I\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_0c1436a5a6a4421ba80398cb\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-006/delta-spec.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-006/delta-spec.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-006: Sandbox 删除与生命周期管理 — Delta Spec\\n2: \\n3: ## Purpose\\n4: \\n5: 为 `pkg/workloadmanager` 模块实现 Sandbox 删除处理器和后台垃圾回收（GC）循环，补全沙箱生命周期的\\\"删除\\\"环节。覆盖 `DELETE /v1/agent-runtime/sessions/:sessionId` 和 `DELETE /v1/code-interpreter/sessions/:sessionId` 端点的 handler 实现、Store 条目清理、CR 删除幂等性、认证场景下的 per-user client 使用、每 15 秒 tick 的 GC 循环、以及优雅关闭时后台 worker 的正确退出。本变更是 AR-005（Sandbox 创建处理器）的下游实现，与 AR-004（HTTP 服务框架）和 sandbox-orchestration spec 对齐。\\n6: \\n7: ## Requirements\\n8: \\n9: ### Requirement: SandboxDeleteHandler 结构体与依赖注入\\n10: \\n11: The system SHALL 定义 `SandboxDeleteHandler` 结构体，封装以下依赖：dynamic client（用于删除 Sandbox/SandboxClaim CR）、Store 接口（用于按 session ID 查询和删除会话条目）、TokenCache（用于认证场景下的用户 client 缓存）、UserClientFactory（可选，EnableAuth 时构建 per-user client）、以及 EnableAuth 标志。Handler SHALL 提供构造函数 `NewSandboxDeleteHandler(deps)` 接收依赖结构体。\\n12: \\n13: #### Scenario: Handler 构造\\n14: \\n15: - **GIVEN** 所有必需依赖（dynamic client、Store）均已初始化\\n16: - **WHEN** `NewSandboxDeleteHandler(deps)` 被调用\\n17: - **THEN** 返回非空的 `*SandboxDeleteHandler` 且所有依赖字段已正确赋值\\n18: \\n19: #### Scenario: 可选依赖为 nil 时不 panic\\n20: \\n21: - **GIVEN** TokenCache 和 UserClientFactory 为 nil（EnableAuth=false 场景）\\n22: - **WHEN** Handler 构造完成\\n23: - **THEN** 不 panic，相关字段为 nil，后续代码路径在 EnableAuth=false 时不访问这些字段\\n24: \\n25: ---\\n26: \\n27: ### Requirement: DELETE /v1/agent-runtime/sessions/:sessionId — AgentRuntime S...\n  Line 19: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775820400856,\"sessionID\":\"ses_288db7c39ffeZ1l0ExGm1Z4v9I\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7724e454001g5x7zamM0Ebogz\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7724cd31001v4mPc43DmfDCeY\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_288db7c39ffeZ1l0ExGm1Z4v9I\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_35ff012c25664bd6acc233bc\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-004/delta-spec.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-004/delta-spec.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-004: WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架 — Delta Spec\\n2: \\n3: ## Purpose\\n4: \\n5: <!-- TODO: 填写 Purpose -->\\n6: \\n7: ## Requirements\\n8: \\n9: <!-- TODO: 填写 Requirements (Gherkin 格式) -->\\n\\n(End of file - total 9 lines)\\n</content>\",\"metadata\":{\"preview\":\"# AR-004: WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架 — Delta Spec\\n\\n## Purpose\\n\\n<!-- TODO: 填写 Purpose -->\\n\\n## Requirements\\n\\n<!-- TODO: 填写 Requirements (Gherkin 格式) -->\",\"truncated\":false,\"loaded\":[]},\"title\":\"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-004/delta-spec.md\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775820400849,\"end\":1775820400855}}}}\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z_logs/AR-007_ST-1.log:\n  Line 10: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775820286674,\"sessionID\":\"ses_288dd0034ffe7A3MpJOphMOwjV\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7723286d0014CB6AjvVxmr2lb\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d77231e0f001k0Hl9c851Eh9e4\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_288dd0034ffe7A3MpJOphMOwjV\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"glob\",\"callID\":\"call_78acd9a912d5485eb4e68b62\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"pattern\":\"**/proposal.md\"},\"output\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-007/proposal.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-006/proposal.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-005/proposal.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-004/proposal.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-003/proposal.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-002/proposal.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-001/proposal.md\",\"metadata\":{\"count\":7,\"truncated\":false},\"title\":\"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775820286656,\"end\":1775820286672}}}}\n  Line 16: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775820294433,\"sessionID\":\"ses_288dd0034ffe7A3MpJOphMOwjV\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7723444b001fzhl6HoH16gmSF\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7723381c001wzmjSrVYvkJjx9\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_288dd0034ffe7A3MpJOphMOwjV\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_ca6ba0a5b1f1479aba711f98\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-005/proposal.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-005/proposal.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-005: Sandbox 创建处理器\\n2: \\n3: ## 概述\\n4: \\n5: 为 `pkg/workloadmanager` 模块实现 Sandbox 创建处理器，处理 `POST /v1/agent-runtime` 和 `POST /v1/code-interpreter` 端点的沙箱创建请求。本变更是 AR-004（HTTP 服务框架）的下游实现，将 HTTP 请求转化为 Kubernetes Sandbox/SandboxClaim CR 资源的创建操作，是 AgentCube 沙箱编排系统的核心控制面逻辑。\\n6: \\n7: ## 元信息\\n8: \\n9: - **Module**: pkg/workloadmanager\\n10: - **Language**: Go\\n11: - **Size**: M\\n12: \\n13: ## 目的\\n14: \\n15: WorkloadManager 作为 AgentCube 的核心控制面组件，需要接收来自 Router、CLI 和 SDK 的沙箱创建请求，并将其转化为 Kubernetes 资源的创建操作。本变更实现完整的沙箱创建流程，包括请求验证、CR 构建、资源创建、状态等待、Pod IP 解析和响应返回，为用户提供端到端的沙箱创建能力。\\n16: \\n17: 具体目标：\\n18: 1. 实现 `POST /v1/agent-runtime` 和 `POST /v1/code-interpreter` 的 handler 函数\\n19: 2. 请求体解析与校验（Kind、Name、Namespace 必填项验证）\\n20: 3. 构建 Sandbox 或 SandboxClaim CR 对象（含 labels、annotations、TTL、idle timeout）\\n21: 4. 通过 dynamic client 创建 Kubernetes 资源\\n22: 5. 注册一次性 watcher 等待 Sandbox 状态变为 \\\"running\\\"（超时 2 分钟）\\n23: 6. Pod IP 解析（优先 sandbox name → 回退 annotation → 回退 label selector）\\n24: 7. Store 层状态同步（StoreSandbox → CreateCR → UpdateSandbox）\\n25: 8. 失败时自动回滚（删除已创建的 CR，超时 30s）\\n26: 9. CodeInterpreter Warm Pool 支持（WarmPoolSize > 0 时创建 SandboxClaim 而非完整 Sandbox）\\n27: 10. Auth 模式处理（AuthMode == picod 时注入 PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY）\\n28: \\n29: ## 范围\\n30: \\n31: ### 包含\\n32: \\n33: 1. **Handler 结构体** — `SandboxCreateHandler` 封装 dynamic client、typed client、informer factory、store、token cache 等依...\n  Line 24: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775820370597,\"sessionID\":\"ses_288dd0034ffe7A3MpJOphMOwjV\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7723815e0019xOFpRRKQhj0Gd\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d77236a07001d7hroGXvzjJBYR\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_288dd0034ffe7A3MpJOphMOwjV\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"call_409048c3ec394fe8bcd6ad81\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"content\":\"# AR-007: K8s Reconciler 控制器\\n\\n## 概述\\n\\n为 `pkg/workloadmanager` 模块实现 Kubernetes Reconciler 控制器，基于 client-go 生成的 Informer/Lister/Typed Client 构建 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter CR 的调和循环。本控制器监听 `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1` API 组下的自定义资源变更事件，将 K8s 资源状态与 Store（Redis/Valkey）中的会话状态进行调和，是 AgentCube 控制面的核心驱动引擎。本变更是 AR-005（Sandbox 创建）和 AR-006（Sandbox 删除）的上游基础设施，为 handler 层提供事件驱动的调和能力。\\n\\n## 元信息\\n\\n- **Module**: pkg/workloadmanager\\n- **Language**: Go\\n- **Size**: L\\n\\n## 目的\\n\\n当前 WorkloadManager 的 handler 层（SandboxCreateHandler、SandboxDeleteHandler）以 HTTP 请求为驱动执行一次性操作，缺少对 Kubernetes 资源状态变化的持续监听和自动调和能力。Reconciler 控制器填补这一空白，实现以下目标：\\n\\n1. 通过 `SharedInformerFactory` 监听 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter CR 的创建、更新、删除事件\\n2. 将 CR 状态变更同步到 Store，保持会话状态与 K8s 资源的一致性\\n3. 处理 Pod 生命周期事件（Pending → Running → Terminated），自动更新 Store 中的 Sandbox 状态\\n4. 实现最终一致性：当 Store 与 K8s 资源状态不一致时，通过调和循环自动修复\\n5. 为 GC 循环提供事件驱动的触发机制（资源删除事件立即触发 Store 清理，而非等待 15s tick）\\n6. 支持优雅启动和关闭：Informer 缓存同步完成后再开始调和，关闭时等待队列中的调和任务完成\\n\\n## 范围\\n\\n### 包含\\n\\n1. **Reconciler 结构体** — `SandboxReconciler` 封装 typed client、informer factory、lister、store、workqueue 等依赖\\n2. **Informer 注册** — 通过 `SharedInformerFactory` 注册 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter 的 informer，设置事件回调（AddFunc、UpdateFunc、DeleteFunc）\\n3. **Workqueue 设计** — 使用 `workqueue.RateLimitingInterface` 作为调和队列，支持指数退避重试（初始 5s，最大 5min，最多 15 次）\\n4. **AgentRuntime 调和逻辑**：\\n   - `OnAdd`：CR 创建事件 → 解析 CR spec → `StoreSandbox` 写入 Store → 记录调和开始\\n   - `OnUpdate`：CR 状态变更事件 → 对比旧/新状态的 `Conditions` → 若 `Ready` 条件变化 → 更新 Store 中对应 session 的状态（Pending → Running → Terminated）→ 若进入 Terminated 状态 → 触发 Store 清理\\n   - `OnDelete`：CR 删除事件 → `DeleteSandboxBySes...\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z_logs/AR-007_ST-0.log:\n  Line 5: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775820227415,\"sessionID\":\"ses_288ddd01effec7QPpbOLxW9gxk\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d772241e10016Ne8PxRsXmFzyj\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d772230c9001CeDT0QLbn0zqhS\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_288ddd01effec7QPpbOLxW9gxk\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"glob\",\"callID\":\"call_be363ae165684d6f8f938a74\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"pattern\":\"**/changes/**\"},\"output\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-006/tasks.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-006/design.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-006/delta-spec.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-006/proposal.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-005/tasks.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-005/delta-spec.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-005/proposal.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-005/design.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-004/tasks.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-004/design.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-004/proposal.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-004/delta-spec.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-003/delta-spec.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-0...\n  Line 10: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775820232830,\"sessionID\":\"ses_288ddd01effec7QPpbOLxW9gxk\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d772253aa001gA3xmimz13UAVe\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d772245e4001uOBDa2vS6uyie1\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_288ddd01effec7QPpbOLxW9gxk\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_0ddd079b744a42e4b7ad4c15\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-006/design.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-006/design.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-006: Sandbox 删除与生命周期管理\\n2: \\n3: ## Overview\\n4: \\n5: 为 `pkg/workloadmanager/handler` 模块实现 Sandbox 删除处理器（`SandboxDeleteHandler`）和后台垃圾回收器（`garbageCollector`），补全沙箱生命周期的\\\"删除\\\"环节。覆盖两个 HTTP DELETE 端点、Store 条目清理、CR 删除幂等性、认证场景下的 per-user client 使用、每 15 秒 tick 的 GC 循环、以及优雅关闭时后台 worker 的正确退出。\\n6: \\n7: 本变更是 AR-005（Sandbox 创建处理器）的下游实现，与 AR-004（HTTP 服务框架）、sandbox-orchestration spec 和 session-store design 对齐。\\n8: \\n9: ## Context\\n10: \\n11: AR-005 实现了 Sandbox 创建流程，但缺少对应的删除能力。当前系统中：\\n12: \\n13: - Sandbox 创建后会在 Store（Redis/Valkey）中存储 `SandboxInfo` 条目，并在 Kubernetes 中创建 Sandbox 或 SandboxClaim CR\\n14: - 没有用户触发的主动删除接口，只能等待 agentd idle-cleanup controller 或 TTL 到期\\n15: - 没有后台垃圾回收机制来清理过期/空闲但未被 agentd 处理的沙箱\\n16: - 进程关闭时没有优雅关闭流程，可能导致 goroutine 泄漏和 Store 连接未释放\\n17: \\n18: AR-006 解决这些问题，提供完整的删除生命周期管理。\\n19: \\n20: ## Goals\\n21: \\n22: 1. 实现 `SandboxDeleteHandler`，支持 `DELETE /v1/agent-runtime/sessions/:sessionId` 和 `DELETE /v1/code-interpreter/sessions/:sessionId`\\n23: 2. 实现后台 `garbageCollector`，每 15 秒 tick 清理过期和空闲沙箱\\n24: 3. CR 删除幂等性（NotFound 视为成功）\\n25: 4. 认证场景下使用 per-user dynamic client（与创建流程一致）\\n26: 5. 优雅关闭：HTTP server → GC goroutine → Store.Close()\\n27: 6. 单元测试覆盖所有错误路径和边界条件\\n28: \\n29: ## Non-Goals\\n30: \\n31: - 不实现 Kubernetes finalizer 机制（生命周期通过 annotations 和 shutdownTime 管理）\\n32: - 不修改 Sandbox CRD 类型定义\\n33: - 不实现批量删除接口\\n34: - 不实现删除审计日志（仅结构化日志）\\n35: \\n36: ## Design\\n37:...\n  Line 11: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775820234202,\"sessionID\":\"ses_288ddd01effec7QPpbOLxW9gxk\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d77225901001GbzSLEMt6ismrZ\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d772245e4001uOBDa2vS6uyie1\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_288ddd01effec7QPpbOLxW9gxk\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_27c7ba9dca7e452f89659c2d\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-006/delta-spec.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-006/delta-spec.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-006: Sandbox 删除与生命周期管理 — Delta Spec\\n2: \\n3: ## Purpose\\n4: \\n5: 为 `pkg/workloadmanager` 模块实现 Sandbox 删除处理器和后台垃圾回收（GC）循环，补全沙箱生命周期的\\\"删除\\\"环节。覆盖 `DELETE /v1/agent-runtime/sessions/:sessionId` 和 `DELETE /v1/code-interpreter/sessions/:sessionId` 端点的 handler 实现、Store 条目清理、CR 删除幂等性、认证场景下的 per-user client 使用、每 15 秒 tick 的 GC 循环、以及优雅关闭时后台 worker 的正确退出。本变更是 AR-005（Sandbox 创建处理器）的下游实现，与 AR-004（HTTP 服务框架）和 sandbox-orchestration spec 对齐。\\n6: \\n7: ## Requirements\\n8: \\n9: ### Requirement: SandboxDeleteHandler 结构体与依赖注入\\n10: \\n11: The system SHALL 定义 `SandboxDeleteHandler` 结构体，封装以下依赖：dynamic client（用于删除 Sandbox/SandboxClaim CR）、Store 接口（用于按 session ID 查询和删除会话条目）、TokenCache（用于认证场景下的用户 client 缓存）、UserClientFactory（可选，EnableAuth 时构建 per-user client）、以及 EnableAuth 标志。Handler SHALL 提供构造函数 `NewSandboxDeleteHandler(deps)` 接收依赖结构体。\\n12: \\n13: #### Scenario: Handler 构造\\n14: \\n15: - **GIVEN** 所有必需依赖（dynamic client、Store）均已初始化\\n16: - **WHEN** `NewSandboxDeleteHandler(deps)` 被调用\\n17: - **THEN** 返回非空的 `*SandboxDeleteHandler` 且所有依赖字段已正确赋值\\n18: \\n19: #### Scenario: 可选依赖为 nil 时不 panic\\n20: \\n21: - **GIVEN** TokenCache 和 UserClientFactory 为 nil（EnableAuth=false 场景）\\n22: - **WHEN** Handler 构造完成\\n23: - **THEN** 不 panic，相关字段为 nil，后续代码路径在 EnableAuth=false 时不访问这些字段\\n24: \\n25: ---\\n26: \\n27: ### Requirement: DELETE /v1/agent-runtime/sessions/:sessionId — AgentRuntime S...\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z_logs/AR-006_ST-7.log:\n  Line 21: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775820194913,\"sessionID\":\"ses_288deaa31ffeVP0mYhQq5K3nsM\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7721b078001pFj16LiAVCZRn4\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d77219c220013vDfHXBqIi1a83\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_288deaa31ffeVP0mYhQq5K3nsM\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_496bd2d55b594ca8a4ad498e\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-006/delta-spec.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-006/delta-spec.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-006: Sandbox 删除与生命周期管理 — Delta Spec\\n2: \\n3: ## Purpose\\n4: \\n5: 为 `pkg/workloadmanager` 模块实现 Sandbox 删除处理器和后台垃圾回收（GC）循环，补全沙箱生命周期的\\\"删除\\\"环节。覆盖 `DELETE /v1/agent-runtime/sessions/:sessionId` 和 `DELETE /v1/code-interpreter/sessions/:sessionId` 端点的 handler 实现、Store 条目清理、CR 删除幂等性、认证场景下的 per-user client 使用、每 15 秒 tick 的 GC 循环、以及优雅关闭时后台 worker 的正确退出。本变更是 AR-005（Sandbox 创建处理器）的下游实现，与 AR-004（HTTP 服务框架）和 sandbox-orchestration spec 对齐。\\n6: \\n7: ## Requirements\\n8: \\n9: ### Requirement: SandboxDeleteHandler 结构体与依赖注入\\n10: \\n11: The system SHALL 定义 `SandboxDeleteHandler` 结构体，封装以下依赖：dynamic client（用于删除 Sandbox/SandboxClaim CR）、Store 接口（用于按 session ID 查询和删除会话条目）、TokenCache（用于认证场景下的用户 client 缓存）、UserClientFactory（可选，EnableAuth 时构建 per-user client）、以及 EnableAuth 标志。Handler SHALL 提供构造函数 `NewSandboxDeleteHandler(deps)` 接收依赖结构体。\\n12: \\n13: #### Scenario: Handler 构造\\n14: \\n15: - **GIVEN** 所有必需依赖（dynamic client、Store）均已初始化\\n16: - **WHEN** `NewSandboxDeleteHandler(deps)` 被调用\\n17: - **THEN** 返回非空的 `*SandboxDeleteHandler` 且所有依赖字段已正确赋值\\n18: \\n19: #### Scenario: 可选依赖为 nil 时不 panic\\n20: \\n21: - **GIVEN** TokenCache 和 UserClientFactory 为 nil（EnableAuth=false 场景）\\n22: - **WHEN** Handler 构造完成\\n23: - **THEN** 不 panic，相关字段为 nil，后续代码路径在 EnableAuth=false 时不访问这些字段\\n24: \\n25: ---\\n26: \\n27: ### Requirement: DELETE /v1/agent-runtime/sessions/:sessionId — AgentRuntime S...\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z_logs/AR-006_ST-4.log:\n  Line 4: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775818838177,\"sessionID\":\"ses_288f65bbcffe5TdygA1wWgT13C\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7709ac59001BEkYFnffVpBKr5\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7709a538001II1mfXH8k5ub46\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_288f65bbcffe5TdygA1wWgT13C\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"task\",\"callID\":\"call_7be025b756ac4d37969e5e14\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"description\":\"Explore agentcube project structure\",\"prompt\":\"Explore the agentcube project structure thoroughly. I need to understand:\\n\\n1. The overall project structure and architecture\\n2. The pkg/workloadmanager module - what files exist, what they do, current implementation\\n3. Any existing sandbox-related code, lifecycle management patterns\\n4. How tasks/checklists are typically structured in this project (look for tasks.md, TODO, or similar files)\\n5. Any existing Stage ST-3 completion artifacts or design documents\\n6. Testing patterns used in the project\\n7. Any related modules or dependencies that interact with workloadmanager\\n\\nSearch broadly across the project. Look for:\\n- pkg/workloadmanager/ directory contents\\n- Any sandbox-related code\\n- Design docs, architecture docs\\n- Existing task lists or checklists\\n- Test files for w