us_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-004/proposal.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-004/proposal.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # Proposal: AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架\\n2: \\n3: ## Purpose\\n4: \\n5: Define the WorkloadManager HTTP service framework for the AgentCube platform. The WorkloadManager provides a Kubernetes-native HTTP API for managing agent runtime workloads, enabling clients to create, query, update, and delete agent runtime instances through a RESTful interface.\\n6: \\n7: The WorkloadManager service provides:\\n8: \\n9: - **HTTP API endpoints** for AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter CRUD operations\\n10: - **Kubernetes client integration** using generated client-go libraries\\n11: - **Request validation and authentication** via JWT/Kubernetes TokenReview\\n12: - **Asynchronous operation support** with status polling\\n13: - **Health checks and metrics** for observability\\n14: \\n15: ## Scope\\n16: \\n17: **Module:** `pkg/workloadmanager`  \\n18: **Language:** Go  \\n19: **Size:** M\\n20: \\n21: ### In Scope\\n22: \\n23: 1. **HTTP Server Setup** (`pkg/workloadmanager/server.go`)\\n24:    - Gin router configuration\\n25:    - Middleware stack (logging, recovery, CORS, auth)\\n26:    - Graceful shutdown handling\\n27:    - Port configuration (default :8080)\\n28: \\n29: 2. **API Handlers** (`pkg/workloadmanager/handlers/`)\\n30:    - `agentruntime.go` — AgentRuntime CRUD endpoints\\n31:    - `codeinterpreter.go` — CodeInterpreter CRUD endpoints\\n32:    - `h...\n  Line 40: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775841123631,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2879fbe5affeDviCnbLKcjMiQx\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d786119f1001qry5w5XtX4nKhH\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d786110c2001fgTBFOU46Cnd24\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2879fbe5affeDviCnbLKcjMiQx\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Now I have enough context to write the design.md for AR-004 (WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架). Let me check if there's a CodeInterpreter type definition I missed.\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775841123630,\"end\":1775841123630}}}\n  Line 48: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775841134343,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2879fbe5affeDviCnbLKcjMiQx\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7861459b001Dnrt0TtSyFlx6h\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7861397d001v0bWXqXY0qyUDO\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2879fbe5affeDviCnbLKcjMiQx\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Now I have comprehensive context. Let me create the design.md file for AR-004 (WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架):\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775841134340,\"end\":1775841134340}}}\n  Line 49: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775841303925,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2879fbe5affeDviCnbLKcjMiQx\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d78614706001QhaqgoPSZy3SYo\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7861397d001v0bWXqXY0qyUDO\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2879fbe5affeDviCnbLKcjMiQx\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"toolu_964feb77e51940419de4fa27\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/pkg/workloadmanager/design.md\",\"content\":\"# AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架 Design\\n\\n## Overview\\n\\n| Item | Value |\\n|------|-------|\\n| AR | AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架 |\\n| Module | `pkg/workloadmanager` |\\n| Language | Go |\\n| Size | M |\\n| Stage | ST-1 completed |\\n\\nWorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架提供 Kubernetes-native 的 HTTP API，用于管理 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter 工作负载。该服务封装了 client-go 的复杂性，为 Python SDK、CLI 工具和其他消费者提供简化的 RESTful 接口。\\n\\n## Architecture\\n\\n### 组件分层\\n\\n```\\nClient (SDK/CLI/Frontend)\\n  ↓ HTTPS\\nGin Router (:8080)\\n  ↓\\nMiddleware Stack\\n  ├─ LoggingMiddleware\\n  ├─ RecoveryMiddleware\\n  ├─ CORSMiddleware\\n  └─ AuthMiddleware (optional)\\n  ↓\\nHTTP Handlers\\n  ├─ AgentRuntime Handlers\\n  ├─ CodeInterpreter Handlers\\n  ├─ Health Handlers\\n  └─ Metrics Handler\\n  ↓\\nService Layer (WorkloadManager Interface)\\n  ↓\\nKubernetes Client Layer\\n  ├─ typed client (AgentRuntimeInterface, CodeInterpreterInterface)\\n  ├─ informers (SharedInformerFactory)\\n  └─ listers (AgentRuntimeLister, CodeInterpreterLister)\\n  ↓\\nKubernetes API Server\\n```\\n\\n### 目录结构\\n\\n```\\npkg/workloadmanager/\\n├── server.go              # Gin server setup, router configuration, graceful shutdown\\n├── service.go             # WorkloadManager interface definition\\n├── client.go              # Kubernetes client initialization\\n├── types.go               # API request/response DTOs\\n├── handlers/\\n│   ├── agentruntime.go    # AgentRuntime CRUD handlers\\n│   ├── codeinterpreter.go # CodeInterpreter CRUD handlers\\n│   ├── health.go          # Health ...\n  Line 52: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775841310073,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2879fbe5affeDviCnbLKcjMiQx\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7863e838001v3Kpv0pdziv3a4\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7863dda8001kGTJiLFVSWMLQ1\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2879fbe5affeDviCnbLKcjMiQx\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Created design.md for AR-004 (WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架) at `pkg/workloadmanager/design.md`. The design includes:\\n\\n- **Architecture**: Component layering, directory structure, startup flow\\n- **Data Structures**: API request/response DTOs, service interface, configuration\\n- **API Contracts**: Complete REST API specification for AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter CRUD, health endpoints\\n- **Error Handling**: Error classification, HTTP mapping, centralized error middleware\\n- **Testing Strategy**: Unit tests, integration tests, mock infrastructure, coverage goals\\n- **client-go Integration**: Client initialization, informer setup, lister usage patterns\\n- **Key Decisions**: Informer vs direct API, Gin vs controller-runtime server, status endpoint rationale\\n- **Configuration**: Environment variables, CLI flags\\n- **Graceful Shutdown**: Shutdown sequence with timeouts\\n- **AR-005 Boundary**: Clear separation of concerns\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775841310071,\"end\":1775841310071}}}\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z_logs/AR-004_ST-0.log:\n  Line 28: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775841299151,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2879ce7dfffexdSxxBgGzWU26c\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7863a586001yrYgfglvZiV63d\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d786395990013joySc3NmWJIZK\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2879ce7dfffexdSxxBgGzWU26c\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"toolu_64f1ad8871ce4a7ca9d0613f\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"content\":\"# Delta Spec: AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架\\n\\n## Overview\\n\\nThis delta-spec defines acceptance scenarios for implementing the WorkloadManager HTTP service framework in `pkg/workloadmanager`.\\n\\n## Base Specifications\\n\\n- **AR**: AR-004\\n- **Module**: `pkg/workloadmanager`\\n- **Language**: Go\\n- **Size**: M\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Scenario: HTTP Server Foundation\\n\\n### AR-004-001: Server initialization\\n\\n- **GIVEN** a Go package at `pkg/workloadmanager`\\n- **WHEN** creating HTTP server initialization\\n- **THEN** the server SHALL embed necessary HTTP handlers\\n- **AND** SHALL expose configurable listen address\\n\\n### AR-004-002: Health check endpoint\\n\\n- **GIVEN** HTTP server running\\n- **WHEN** health check endpoint is accessed\\n- **THEN** it SHALL return appropriate health status\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Scenario: Workload Management API\\n\\n### AR-004-003: Create workload endpoint\\n\\n- **GIVEN** HTTP server with workload management\\n- **WHEN** POST request to create workload\\n- **THEN** the workload SHALL be created successfully\\n\\n### AR-004-004: Get workload endpoint\\n\\n- **GIVEN** existing workloads\\n- **WHEN** GET request for specific workload\\n- **THEN** it SHALL return workload details\\n\\n### AR-004-005: List workloads endpoint\\n\\n- **GIVEN** multiple workloads exist\\n- **WHEN** GET request to list workloads\\n- **THEN** it SHALL return all workloads\\n\\n---\\n\\n## References\\n\",\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-004/delta-spec.md\"},\"output\":\"Wrote file successfully.\",\"metadata\":{\"diagnostics\":{},\"filepath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/openc...\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z_logs/AR-003_ST-4.log:\n  Line 10: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775841175115,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2879e34cfffeVEXMbQEUVmsl00\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7861e61a001EuA2sqXqH6K4Ss\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7861dcc8001m9JoFlmkVjB8RU\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2879e34cfffeVEXMbQEUVmsl00\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-bb00dca29239417cb366d5a5e2d26ac7\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/project.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/project.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AgentCube — OpenSpec Project Context\\n2: \\n3: > Source: [github.com/ShijunDeng/agentcube](https://github.com/ShijunDeng/agentcube)\\n4: > Generated: 2026-03-21 (from source tree reverse-engineering)\\n5: \\n6: ## Purpose\\n7: \\n8: AgentCube is a Kubernetes-native sandbox orchestration platform for AI agents.\\n9: It provisions isolated sandbox pods on demand, routes HTTP traffic to them through\\n10: session-aware proxies, and manages their lifecycle (creation, expiry, idle cleanup).\\n11: \\n12: ## Tech Stack\\n13: \\n14: | Layer | Technology |\\n15: |-------|-----------|\\n16: | Language (server) | Go 1.24, module `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube` |\\n17: | Language (CLI/SDK) | Python ≥3.10 |\\n18: | HTTP framework | Gin (Go), Typer (Python CLI), FastAPI (example) |\\n19: | Kubernetes | CRDs (`runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`), controller-runtime, `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox` |\\n20: | Storage | Redis (go-redis/v9), Valkey (valkey-go) |\\n21: | Auth | JWT RS256 (golang-jwt/v5), K8s TokenReview |\\n22: | Packaging | Helm 3, multi-stage Docker, GitHub Actions CI/CD |\\n23: | Docs | Docusaurus 3.x |\\n24: \\n25: ## Architecture\\n26: \\n27: ```\\n28: Client / SDK / CLI\\n29:   → Router (Deployment :8080)\\n30:      ↔ Redis/Valkey (session store)\\n31:      → WorkloadManager (Service :8080)\\n32:         ↔ Redis/Valkey\\n33:         → K8s API: CRDs, Sandbox, Pod, Secret, T...\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z_logs/AR-016_ST-1.log:\n  Line 13: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775841092261,\"sessionID\":\"ses_287a02d82ffewOT6YoU0ctMuc9\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d78609f85001vBG6Lnu7WD3OBY\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7860939f001OLtHS614ZNCUYh\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_287a02d82ffewOT6YoU0ctMuc9\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_2b099387c89149e39c9547ad\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/proposal.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/proposal.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-011: Router JWT 认证与签发\\n2: \\n3: ## Purpose\\n4: \\n5: 为 AgentCube Router 添加完整的 JWT 认证与签发能力，实现双向安全通信：\\n6: \\n7: 1. **入站认证（Inbound Authentication）**：Router 自身的 API 端点需要验证调用方身份，防止未授权访问。当前 Router 的所有 `/v1` 路由均无认证保护，任何网络可达的客户端均可直接调用 sandbox 资源。\\n8: 2. **出站签发（Outbound Signing）**：Router 向下游 Sandbox/PicoD 转发请求时，签发 JWT 作为服务间身份凭证，确保下游服务能验证请求来源为合法的 Router 实例。\\n9: \\n10: 现有代码已实现出站签发（`jwt.go` + `proxy.go` 中的 token 注入），但缺失入站认证。本 AR 补全认证链路，满足 `testing/agentcube_tdd_manifest.md` 中定义的 `AuthMiddleware` 测试用例（Test-RT-1: 无效 JWT 返回 401，Test-RT-2: 过期 JWT 返回 \\\"Token Expired\\\"）。\\n11: \\n12: ## Scope\\n13: \\n14: ### In Scope\\n15: \\n16: 1. **AuthMiddleware 实现**\\n17:    - 新增 `AuthMiddleware() gin.HandlerFunc` 方法，验证请求 `Authorization: Bearer <token>` 头\\n18:    - 使用 RSA 公钥验证 RS256 签名（拒绝 HMAC 等弱签名算法）\\n19:    - 强制校验 `exp`（过期时间）和 `iat`（签发时间）claim\\n20:    - 配置 1 分钟时钟容差（leeway），容忍分布式系统中的时钟偏移\\n21:    - 验证失败返回标准化 401 响应：`{\\\"error\\\": \\\"<message>\\\", \\\"code\\\": \\\"<error_code>\\\"}`\\n22: \\n23: 2. **JWTManager 扩展**\\n24:    - 在现有 `JWTManager` 上增加 `PublicKey()` 方法，供认证中间件获取验证用的公钥\\n25:    - 新增 `ParseAndValidateToken(tokenString string) (*jwt.Token, error)` 方法用于验证入站 token\\n26:    - 复用已有的 K8s Secret 密钥持久化机制（`picod-router-identity`），无需新建密钥存储\\n27:    - 非集群环境下使用临时密钥对（与现有行为一致，记录 warning 日志）\\n28: \\n29: 3. **路由保护**\\n30:    - 将 `AuthMiddleware` 应用于 `/v1` 路由组（与现有 `ConcurrencyLimitMiddleware` 同级）\\n31:    - 健康检查端点（`/health/live`、`/...\n  Line 15: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775841094597,\"sessionID\":\"ses_287a02d82ffewOT6YoU0ctMuc9\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7860a76f0015SuYvZ2ol8M6Lz\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7860939f001OLtHS614ZNCUYh\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_287a02d82ffewOT6YoU0ctMuc9\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_893cd8a47d09482e90715234\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-015/proposal.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-015/proposal.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-015 — PicoD 命令执行 API\\n2: \\n3: **Module:** pkg/picod\\n4: **Language:** Go\\n5: **Size:** M\\n6: \\n7: ## 目的\\n8: \\n9: PicoD 是运行在每个沙箱 Pod 内部的轻量级命令执行守护进程，负责接收 JWT 认证的 HTTP 请求，在可配置的工作空间沙箱（workspace jail）内执行命令、管理文件，并提供健康检查端点。本变更将创建 `pkg/picod` 包和 `cmd/picod` 入口，实现完整的 API 服务，是 AgentCube 代码执行能力的核心组件。\\n10: \\n11: ## 范围\\n12: \\n13: ### 包含\\n14: 1. **包结构** — 创建 `pkg/picod/` 目录，包含 server、auth、execute、files 四个子模块\\n15: 2. **入口程序** — `cmd/picod/main.go`，解析 CLI 标志、构建 Config、启动服务\\n16: 3. **HTTP 路由** — Gin 框架注册 `/api/execute`、`/api/files`（上传/列表/下载）、`/health` 端点\\n17: 4. **JWT 认证** — RSA 公钥验证中间件，保护所有 `/api` 路由，`/health` 无需认证\\n18: 5. **命令执行** — `exec.CommandContext` 带超时控制，捕获 stdout/stderr，返回结构化响应\\n19: 6. **文件管理** — multipart 上传、Base64 JSON 上传、目录列表、文件下载\\n20: 7. **路径安全** — `sanitizePath` 防止目录穿越，确保所有文件操作限制在 workspace jail 内\\n21: 8. **CLI 标志** — `-port`（默认 8080）、`-workspace`（默认 CWD）\\n22: 9. **环境变量** — `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY`（PEM 编码 RSA 公钥，启动时必填）\\n23: \\n24: ### 不包含\\n25: - JWT 密钥对的生成和管理（由 Router 组件负责，通过 K8s Secret `picod-router-identity` 存储）\\n26: - 公钥注入逻辑（由 WorkloadManager 的 `injectPicodAuthEnv` 负责）\\n27: - Docker 镜像构建配置（Dockerfile 已在部署设计中定义）\\n28: - Helm Chart 模板（属于部署变更）\\n29: \\n30: ## 架构概要\\n31: \\n32: ```\\n33: cmd/picod/main.go\\n34:   └── pkg/picod/\\n35:         ├── config.go       — Config struct, CLI flag parsing\\n36:         ├── server.go       — Server struct, NewS...\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z_logs/AR-004_ST-2.log:\n  Line 4: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775841058665,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2879ff1c8ffel6rnr8XkDcFUTt\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d78601ad0001NYOGGw5YBHu962\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d78600f2c001f0U0MklSWFx88U\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2879ff1c8ffel6rnr8XkDcFUTt\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_a4569670edd847f893fc7ee5\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/.sdd_prompt.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/.sdd_prompt.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: Write delta-spec.md (GIVEN/WHEN/THEN scenarios) for the agentcube project:\\n2: \\n3: AR: AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架\\n4: Module: pkg/workloadmanager\\n5: Language: Go\\n6: Size: M\\n7: \\n8: Base specs:\\n9: --- deployment/client-go.md ---\\n10: # client-go library\\n11: \\n12: Generated Kubernetes client code for API group **`runtime.agentcube.volcano.