rConfig(c *rest.Config) (*Clientset, error)`\\n32: - `NewForConfigAndClient(c *rest.Config, httpClient *http.Client) (*Clientset, error)`\\n33: - `NewForConfigOrDie(c *rest.Config) *Clientset`\\n34: - `New(c rest.Interface) *Clientset`\\n35: \\n36: **Group accessor:** `RuntimeV1alpha1() runtimev1alpha1.RuntimeV1alpha1Interface`\\n37: \\n38: ---\\n39: \\n40: ## Typed client — `runtime/v1alpha1`\\n41: \\n42: ### `RuntimeV1alpha1Interface` (`clientset/ve...\n  Line 25: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775841002706,\"sessionID\":\"ses_287a1485cffe8cC5b5mQ4ByNoH\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d785f4053001LH4pQ02r0hpS7S\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d785f30f10011Y9E0A9iYjg2kP\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_287a1485cffe8cC5b5mQ4ByNoH\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_58331cae00ca4b5f9d5f8b78\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/project.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/project.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AgentCube — OpenSpec Project Context\\n2: \\n3: > Source: [github.com/ShijunDeng/agentcube](https://github.com/ShijunDeng/agentcube)\\n4: > Generated: 2026-03-21 (from source tree reverse-engineering)\\n5: \\n6: ## Purpose\\n7: \\n8: AgentCube is a Kubernetes-native sandbox orchestration platform for AI agents.\\n9: It provisions isolated sandbox pods on demand, routes HTTP traffic to them through\\n10: session-aware proxies, and manages their lifecycle (creation, expiry, idle cleanup).\\n11: \\n12: ## Tech Stack\\n13: \\n14: | Layer | Technology |\\n15: |-------|-----------|\\n16: | Language (server) | Go 1.24, module `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube` |\\n17: | Language (CLI/SDK) | Python ≥3.10 |\\n18: | HTTP framework | Gin (Go), Typer (Python CLI), FastAPI (example) |\\n19: | Kubernetes | CRDs (`runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`), controller-runtime, `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox` |\\n20: | Storage | Redis (go-redis/v9), Valkey (valkey-go) |\\n21: | Auth | JWT RS256 (golang-jwt/v5), K8s TokenReview |\\n22: | Packaging | Helm 3, multi-stage Docker, GitHub Actions CI/CD |\\n23: | Docs | Docusaurus 3.x |\\n24: \\n25: ## Architecture\\n26: \\n27: ```\\n28: Client / SDK / CLI\\n29:   → Router (Deployment :8080)\\n30:      ↔ Redis/Valkey (session store)\\n31:      → WorkloadManager (Service :8080)\\n32:         ↔ Redis/Valkey\\n33:         → K8s API: CRDs, Sandbox, Pod, Secret, Toke...\n  Line 28: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775841006501,\"sessionID\":\"ses_287a1485cffe8cC5b5mQ4ByNoH\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d785f4d43001pSW2Bo83qdF990\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d785f450b0010uI70YCHpNr3uL\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_287a1485cffe8cC5b5mQ4ByNoH\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Based on the existing proposal templates and the specification provided, I'll create the proposal for AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架.\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775841006500,\"end\":1775841006500}}}\n  Line 29: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775841048209,\"sessionID\":\"ses_287a1485cffe8cC5b5mQ4ByNoH\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d785f53a6001U3X6h0K20L0MaS\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d785f450b0010uI70YCHpNr3uL\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_287a1485cffe8cC5b5mQ4ByNoH\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"toolu_59b3cf2e4ac4486dab39e579\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-004/proposal.md\",\"content\":\"# Proposal: AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架\\n\\n## Purpose\\n\\nDefine the WorkloadManager HTTP service framework for the AgentCube platform. The WorkloadManager provides a Kubernetes-native HTTP API for managing agent runtime workloads, enabling clients to create, query, update, and delete agent runtime instances through a RESTful interface.\\n\\nThe WorkloadManager service provides:\\n\\n- **HTTP API endpoints** for AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter CRUD operations\\n- **Kubernetes client integration** using generated client-go libraries\\n- **Request validation and authentication** via JWT/Kubernetes TokenReview\\n- **Asynchronous operation support** with status polling\\n- **Health checks and metrics** for observability\\n\\n## Scope\\n\\n**Module:** `pkg/workloadmanager`  \\n**Language:** Go  \\n**Size:** M\\n\\n### In Scope\\n\\n1. **HTTP Server Setup** (`pkg/workloadmanager/server.go`)\\n   - Gin router configuration\\n   - Middleware stack (logging, recovery, CORS, auth)\\n   - Graceful shutdown handling\\n   - Port configuration (default :8080)\\n\\n2. **API Handlers** (`pkg/workloadmanager/handlers/`)\\n   - `agentruntime.go` — AgentRuntime CRUD endpoints\\n   - `codeinterpreter.go` — CodeInterpreter CRUD endpoints\\n   - `health.go` — Health check endpoints (`/healthz`, `/readyz`)\\n   - `metrics.go` — Prometheus metrics endpoint\\n\\n3. **Request/Response Types** (`pkg/workloadmanager/types.go`)\\n   - API request DTOs\\n   - API response DTOs\\n   - Error response format\\n   - Pagination types\\n\\n4. **Kubernet...\n  Line 32: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775841052149,\"sessionID\":\"ses_287a1485cffe8cC5b5mQ4ByNoH\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d786003ad001hYJs1AomMMG75f\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d785ff6c6001Rae3Jv33pOqWQV\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_287a1485cffe8cC5b5mQ4ByNoH\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Done. The proposal for AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架 has been created at `/changes/AR-004/proposal.md`.\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775841052148,\"end\":1775841052148}}}\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z_logs/AR-016_ST-0.log:\n  Line 12: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775841001969,\"sessionID\":\"ses_287a0efabffeIMy3BqCl3A3yvx\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d785f3da000134kIYw5va83z9m\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d785f3692001wF54bigBXb1wjI\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_287a0efabffeIMy3BqCl3A3yvx\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_6daea81f912b417eb6ef8df8\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-015/proposal.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-015/proposal.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-015 — PicoD 命令执行 API\\n2: \\n3: **Module:** pkg/picod\\n4: **Language:** Go\\n5: **Size:** M\\n6: \\n7: ## 目的\\n8: \\n9: PicoD 是运行在每个沙箱 Pod 内部的轻量级命令执行守护进程，负责接收 JWT 认证的 HTTP 请求，在可配置的工作空间沙箱（workspace jail）内执行命令、管理文件，并提供健康检查端点。本变更将创建 `pkg/picod` 包和 `cmd/picod` 入口，实现完整的 API 服务，是 AgentCube 代码执行能力的核心组件。\\n10: \\n11: ## 范围\\n12: \\n13: ### 包含\\n14: 1. **包结构** — 创建 `pkg/picod/` 目录，包含 server、auth、execute、files 四个子模块\\n15: 2. **入口程序** — `cmd/picod/main.go`，解析 CLI 标志、构建 Config、启动服务\\n16: 3. **HTTP 路由** — Gin 框架注册 `/api/execute`、`/api/files`（上传/列表/下载）、`/health` 端点\\n17: 4. **JWT 认证** — RSA 公钥验证中间件，保护所有 `/api` 路由，`/health` 无需认证\\n18: 5. **命令执行** — `exec.CommandContext` 带超时控制，捕获 stdout/stderr，返回结构化响应\\n19: 6. **文件管理** — multipart 上传、Base64 JSON 上传、目录列表、文件下载\\n20: 7. **路径安全** — `sanitizePath` 防止目录穿越，确保所有文件操作限制在 workspace jail 内\\n21: 8. **CLI 标志** — `-port`（默认 8080）、`-workspace`（默认 CWD）\\n22: 9. **环境变量** — `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY`（PEM 编码 RSA 公钥，启动时必填）\\n23: \\n24: ### 不包含\\n25: - JWT 密钥对的生成和管理（由 Router 组件负责，通过 K8s Secret `picod-router-identity` 存储）\\n26: - 公钥注入逻辑（由 WorkloadManager 的 `injectPicodAuthEnv` 负责）\\n27: - Docker 镜像构建配置（Dockerfile 已在部署设计中定义）\\n28: - Helm Chart 模板（属于部署变更）\\n29: \\n30: ## 架构概要\\n31: \\n32: ```\\n33: cmd/picod/main.go\\n34:   └── pkg/picod/\\n35:         ├── config.go       — Config struct, CLI flag parsing\\n36:         ├── server.go       — Server struct, NewS...\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z_logs/AR-015_ST-7.log:\n  Line 4: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":17