y (session store)\\n31:      → WorkloadManager (Service :8080)\\n32:         ↔ Redis/Valkey\\n33:         → K8s API: CRDs, Sandbox, Pod, Secret, TokenReview\\n34: ...\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z_logs/AR-002_ST-1.log:\n  Line 13: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775839885336,\"sessionID\":\"ses_287b1fdb0ffeNCtszLkqEWTfOh\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d784e35e3001BKbND49Hy3emGq\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d784e2de7001dUq6quvSUjmlvE\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_287b1fdb0ffeNCtszLkqEWTfOh\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-5697c4f6baa4401589aa77e1339a33f6\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/proposal.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/proposal.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-001: CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义\\n2: \\n3: ## Overview\\n4: \\n5: 定义 AgentRuntime 自定义资源定义（CRD），用于在 Kubernetes 中声明 agent 运行时实例的配置和状态。\\n6: \\n7: ## Purpose\\n8: \\n9: 为 AgentCube 平台提供 AgentRuntime CRD 的 Go 类型定义，包括 API 组、版本、Schema 和 OpenAPI 验证规则。\\n10: \\n11: ## Module\\n12: \\n13: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1`\\n14: \\n15: ## Language\\n16: \\n17: Go 1.24\\n18: \\n19: ## Size\\n20: \\n21: S\\n22: \\n23: ## Scope\\n24: \\n25: ### In Scope\\n26: \\n27: 1. **AgentRuntime CRD 类型定义**\\n28:    - `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1` API 组\\n29:    - Namespaced 作用域\\n30:    - Go 结构体定义（Spec 和 Status）\\n31:    - OpenAPIV3Schema 验证规则\\n32:    - 默认值设置\\n33:    - 打印列（Age）\\n34: \\n35: 2. **Required Spec 字段**\\n36:    - `maxSessionDuration` (string, 默认 \\\"8h\\\")\\n37:    - `sessionTimeout` (string, 默认 \\\"15m\\\")\\n38:    - `targetPort` (TargetPort 数组)\\n39:    - `podTemplate` (PodTemplateSpec)\\n40: \\n41: 3. **Status 字段**\\n42:    - Conditions 集合\\n43:    - 其他状态信息\\n44: \\n45: ### Out of Scope\\n46: \\n47: - Controller 实现\\n48: - Webhook 验证\\n49: - CRD YAML 生成（由 controller-gen 处理）\\n50: - CodeInterpreter CRD（AR-002）\\n51: \\n52: ## Impact Analysis\\n53: \\n54: ### Components Impacted\\n55: \\n56: 1. **Workload Manager**\\n57:    - 需要读取 AgentRuntime 资源\\n58:    - 基于 AgentRuntime spec 创建 agent-sandbox Sandbox\\n59:    - 更新 AgentRuntime status\\n60: \\n61: 2. **Client-Go Library**\\n62:    - 生成的 TypedClient 包含 AgentRuntimeInte...\n  Line 17: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775839943025,\"sessionID\":\"ses_287b1fdb0ffeNCtszLkqEWTfOh\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d784f1912001fPX1x3I18ZLqSR\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d784e386f0013RcQsmbkwOKSuV\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_287b1fdb0ffeNCtszLkqEWTfOh\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-8327454df72a4403b18ab8d12d7737f3\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"content\":\"# AR-001: CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义\\n\\n## Overview\\n\\n定义 AgentRuntime 自定义资源定义（CRD），用于在 Kubernetes 中声明 agent 运行时实例的配置和状态。\\n\\n## Purpose\\n\\n为 AgentCube 平台提供 AgentRuntime CRD 的 Go 类型定义，包括 API 组、版本、Schema 和 OpenAPI 验证规则。\\n\\n## Module\\n\\n`pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1`\\n\\n## Language\\n\\nGo 1.24\\n\\n## Size\\n\\nS\\n\\n## Scope\\n\\n### In Scope\\n\\n1. **AgentRuntime CRD 类型定义**\\n   - `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1` API 组\\n   - Namespaced 作用域\\n   - Go 结构体定义（Spec 和 Status）\\n   - OpenAPIV3Schema 验证规则\\n   - 默认值设置\\n   - 打印列（Age）\\n\\n2. **Required Spec 字段**\\n   - `maxSessionDuration` (string, 默认 \\\"8h\\\")\\n   - `sessionTimeout` (string, 默认 \\\"15m\\\")\\n   - `targetPort` (TargetPort 数组)\\n   - `podTemplate` (PodTemplateSpec)\\n\\n3. **Status 字段**\\n   - Conditions 集合\\n   - 其他状态信息\\n\\n### Out of Scope\\n\\n- Controller 实现\\n- Webhook 验证\\n- CRD YAML 生成（由 controller-gen 处理）\\n- CodeInterpreter CRD（AR-002）\\n\\n## Impact Analysis\\n\\n### Components Impacted\\n\\n1. **Workload Manager**\\n   - 需要读取 AgentRuntime 资源\\n   - 基于 AgentRuntime spec 创建 agent-sandbox Sandbox\\n   - 更新 AgentRuntime status\\n\\n2. **Client-Go Library**\\n   - 生成的 TypedClient 包含 AgentRuntimeInterface\\n   - Informer factory 支持 AgentRuntime 监听\\n   - Lister 提供 AgentRuntime 查询\\n\\n3. **Helm Chart**\\n   - CRD YAML 在 `manifests/charts/base/crds/` 下\\n   - CRD 随 chart 生命周期安装\\n\\n4. **RBAC**\\n   - WorkloadManager ClusterRole 包含 `agentruntimes` 的读权限\\n   - `agentruntimes/status` 的更新权限\\n\\n### Dependencies\\n\\n- `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/apiserver/v1alpha1` (或类似的基础类型)\\n- `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1`\\n- `k8s.io/api/core/v1` (用于 PodSpec 引用)\\n\\n## Design Decisions\\n\\n### API Group and Versio...\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z_logs/AR-001_ST-5.log:\n  Line 18: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775839398480,\"sessionID\":\"ses_287b9a654ffeytIXZNa7Q03JxB\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7846c5d1001mw7sTE0L9JWy3v\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7846af190018rETkvHgc1matI\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_287b9a654ffeytIXZNa7Q03JxB\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"bash\",\"callID\":\"toolu_functions.bash:8\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"command\":\"cat /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/project.md\",\"description\":\"Read project overview\"},\"output\":\"# AgentCube — OpenSpec Project Context\\n\\n> Source: [github.com/ShijunDeng/agentcube](https://github.com/ShijunDeng/agentcube)\\n> Generated: 2026-03-21 (from source tree reverse-engineering)\\n\\n## Purpose\\n\\nAgentCube is a Kubernetes-native sandbox orchestration platform for AI agents.\\nIt provisions isolated sandbox pods on demand, routes HTTP traffic to them through\\nsession-aware proxies, and manages their lifecycle (creation, expiry, idle cleanup).\\n\\n## Tech Stack\\n\\n| Layer | Technology |\\n|-------|-----------|\\n| Language (server) | Go 1.24, module `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube` |\\n| Language (CLI/SDK) | Python ≥3.10 |\\n| HTTP framework | Gin (Go), Typer (Python CLI), FastAPI (example) |\\n| Kubernetes | CRDs (`runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`), controller-runtime, `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox` |\\n| Storage | Redis (go-redis/v9), Valkey (valkey-go) |\\n| Auth | JWT RS256 (golang-jwt/v5), K8s TokenReview |\\n| Packaging | Helm 3, multi-stage Docker, GitHub Actions CI/CD |\\n| Docs | Docusaurus 3.x |\\n\\n## Architecture\\n\\n```\\nClient / SDK / CLI\\n  → Router (Deployment :8080)\\n     ↔ Redis/Valkey (session store)\\n     → WorkloadManager (Service :8080)\\n        ↔ Redis/Valkey\\n        → K8s API: CRDs, Sandbox, Pod, Secret, TokenReview\\n  Sandbox Pods (with optional PicoD daemon)\\n  Agentd (idle cleanup controller)\\n  Optional: Volcano vc-agent-scheduler\\n```\\n\\n## Conventions\\n\\n- Go packages under `pkg/`, binaries under `cmd/`\\n- Python CLI at `cmd/cli/`, SDK at `sdk-p...\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z_logs/AR-001_ST-5.log:\n  Line 26: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775839158729,\"sessionID\":\"ses_287bd30b5ffeEecEG6tiobwWrM\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d784321b2001I4z0U9MvmpDNBd\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d78431306001vj2EEIdIO3bd5Q\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_287bd30b5ffeEecEG6tiobwWrM\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-4d34d4fecd6a46da8dc1c4560d149ed6\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/project.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/project.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AgentCube — OpenSpec Project Context\\n2: \\n3: > Source: [github.com/ShijunDeng/agentcube](https://github.com/ShijunDeng/agentcube)\\n4: > Generated: 2026-03-21 (from source tree reverse-engineering)\\n5: \\n6: ## Purpose\\n7: \\n8: AgentCube is a Kubernetes-native sandbox orchestration platform for AI agents.\\n9: It provisions isolated sandbox pods on demand, routes HTTP traffic to them through\\n10: session-aware proxies, and manages their lifecycle (creation, expiry, idle cleanup).\\n11: \\n12: ## Tech Stack\\n13: \\n14: | Layer | Technology |\\n15: |-------|-----------|\\n16: | Language (server) | Go 1.24, module `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube` |\\n17: | Language (CLI/SDK) | Python ≥3.10 |\\n18: | HTTP framework | Gin (Go), Typer (Python CLI), FastAPI (example) |\\n19: | Kubernetes | CRDs (`runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`), controller-runtime, `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox` |\\n20: | Storage | Redis (go-redis/v9), Valkey (valkey-go) |\\n21: | Auth | JWT RS256 (golang-jwt/v5), K8s TokenReview |\\n22: | Packaging | Helm 3, multi-stage Docker, GitHub Actions CI/CD |\\n23: | Docs | Docusaurus 3.x |\\n24: \\n25: ## Architecture\\n26: \\n27: ```\\n28: Client / SDK / CLI\\n29:   → Router (Deployment :8080)\\n30:      ↔ Redis/Valkey (session store)\\n31:      → WorkloadManager (Service :8080)\\n32:         ↔ Redis/Valkey\\n33:         → K8s API: CRDs, Sandbox, Pod, Secret, T...\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z_logs/AR-001_ST-5.log:\n  Line 9: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775839210656,\"sessionID\":\"ses_287bc4725ffeYyDVPatJ9Fx5O2\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7843ec640013QXzn7h5tqGU2l\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7843d0e8001F2DbtK949WoI0i\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_287bc4725ffeYyDVPatJ9Fx5O2\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-1ab99013853a4c94bd09a2ab2be9c356\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/project.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/project.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AgentCube — OpenSpec Project Context\\n2: \\n3: > Source: [github.com/ShijunDeng/agentcube](https://github.com/ShijunDeng/agentcube)\\n4: > Generated: 2026-03-21 (from source tree reverse-engineering)\\n5: \\n6: ## Purpose\\n7: \\n8: AgentCube is a Kubernetes-native sandbox orchestration platform for AI agents.\\n9: It provisions isolated sandbox pods on demand, routes HTTP traffic to them through\\n10: session-aware proxies, and manages their lifecycle (creation, expiry, idle cleanup).\\n11: \\n12: ## Tech Stack\\n13: \\n14: | Layer | Technology |\\n15: |-------|-----------|\\n16: | Language (server) | Go 1.24, module `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube` |\\n17: | Language (CLI/SDK) | Python ≥3.10 |\\n18: | HTTP framework | Gin (Go), Typer (Python CLI), FastAPI (example) |\\n19: | Kubernetes | CRDs (`runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`), controller-runtime, `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox` |\\n20: | Storage | Redis (go-redis/v9), Valkey (valkey-go) |\\n21: | Auth | JWT RS256 (golang-jwt/v5), K8s TokenReview |\\n22: | Packaging | Helm 3, multi-stage Docker, GitHub Actions CI/CD |\\n23: | Docs | Docusaurus 3.x |\\n24: \\n25: ## Architecture\\n26: \\n27: ```\\n28: Client / SDK / CLI\\n29:   → Router (Deployment :8080)\\n30:      ↔ Redis/Valkey (session store)\\n31:      → WorkloadManager (Service :8080)\\n32:         ↔ Redis/Valkey\\n33:         → K8s API: CRDs, Sandbox, Pod, Secret, Token...\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z_logs/AR-015_ST-4.log:\n  Line 7: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775839401250,\"sessionID\":\"ses_287bcb93dffe74sqV2FOvjBYfr\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7846d16b001E1uAON0cUuY6Dl\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7846bd12001EMAPfRSNd3KqU7\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_287bcb93dffe74sqV2FOvjBYfr\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_9b9a54503a194ef2ba212947\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-015/proposal.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-015/proposal.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-015 — PicoD 命令执行 API\\n2: \\n3: **Module:** pkg/picod\\n4: **Language:** Go\\n5: **Size:** M\\n6: \\n7: ## 目的\\n8: \\n9: PicoD 是运行在每个沙箱 Pod 内部的轻量级命令执行守护进程，负责接收 JWT 认证的 HTTP 请求，在可配置的工作空间沙箱（workspace jail）内执行命令、管理文件，并提供健康检查端点。本变更将创建 `pkg/picod` 包和 `cmd/picod` 入口，实现完整的 API 服务，是 AgentCube 代码执行能力的核心组件。\\n10: \\n11: ## 范围\\n12: \\n13: ### 包含\\n14: 1. **包结构** — 创建 `pkg/picod/` 目录，包含 server、auth、execute、files 四个子模块\\n15: 2. **入口程序** — `cmd/picod/main.go`，解析 CLI 标志、构建 Config、启动服务\\n16: 3. **HTTP 路由** — Gin 框架注册 `/api/execute`、`/api/files`（上传/列表/下载）、`/health` 端点\\n17: 4. **JWT 认证** — RSA 公钥验证中间件，保护所有 `/api` 路由，`/health` 无需认证\\n18: 5. **命令执行** — `exec.CommandContext` 带超时控制，捕获 stdout/stderr，返回结构化响应\\n19: 6. **文件管理** — multipart 上传、Base64 JSON 上传、目录列表、文件下载\\n20: 7. **路径安全** — `sanitizePath` 防止目录穿越，确保所有文件操作限制在 workspace jail 内\\n21: 8. **CLI 标志** — `-port`（默认 8080）、`-workspace`（默认 CWD）\\n22: 9. **环境变量** — `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY`（PEM 编码 RSA 公钥，启动时必填）\\n23: \\n24: ### 不包含\\n25: - JWT 密钥对的生成和管理（由 Router 组件负责，通过 K8s Secret `picod-router-identity` 存储）\\n26: - 公钥注入逻辑（由 WorkloadManager 的 `injectPicodAuthEnv` 负责）\\n27: - Docker 镜像构建配置（Dockerfile 已在部署设计中定义）\\n28: - Helm Chart 模板（属于部署变更）\\n29: \\n30: ## 架构概要\\n31: \\n32: ```\\n33: cmd/picod/main.go\\n34:   └── pkg/picod/\\n35:         ├── config.go       — Config struct, CLI flag parsing\\n36:         ├── server.go       — Server struct, NewS...\n  Line 15: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775839411128,\"sessionID\":\"ses_287bcb93dffe74sqV2FOvjBYfr\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7846f72d001TnUqhqFIW0481S\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7846e1fb001JYA0zYmWzfsl0X\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_287bcb93dffe74sqV2FOvjBYfr\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_b6b4330b614b4f3e972d2106\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-009/tasks.md\"},