yped client (AgentRuntimeInterface, CodeInterpreterInterface)\\n40:   ├─ informers (SharedInformerFactory)\\n41:   └─ listers (AgentRuntimeLister, CodeInterpreterLister)\\n42:   ↓\\n43: Kubernetes API Server\\n44: ```\\n45: \\n46: ### 目录结构\\n47: \\n48: ```\\n49: pkg/workloadmanager/\\n50: ├── server.go              # Gin server setup, router configuration, graceful s... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n11: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775841327131,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2879c023bffeQf7J1q9dvjfwyr\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7864228b0018XzhtyME5HVo8B\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d786411ec00127CeZDK57BbHsD\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2879c023bffeQf7J1q9dvjfwyr\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_58e09a0d3de74680adef8ee0\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-004/proposal.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-004/proposal.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # Proposal: AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架\\n2: \\n3: ## Purpose\\n4: \\n5: Define the WorkloadManager HTTP service framework for the AgentCube platform. The WorkloadManager provides a Kubernetes-native HTTP API for managing agent runtime workloads, enabling clients to create, query, update, and delete agent runtime instances through a RESTful interface.\\n6: \\n7: The WorkloadManager service provides:\\n8: \\n9: - **HTTP API endpoints** for AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter CRUD operations\\n10: - **Kubernetes client integration** using generated client-go libraries\\n11: - **Request validation and authentication** via JWT/Kubernetes TokenReview\\n12: - **Asynchronous operation support** with status polling\\n13: - **Health checks and metrics** for observability\\n14: \\n15: ## Scope\\n16: \\n17: **Module:** `pkg/workloadmanager`  \\n18: **Language:** Go  \\n19: 